===Etymology===
{{PIE root|en|lewh₃}}
From {{etyl|enm|en}} {{m|enm|absolucion}}, {{m|enm|absolucioun}}, from {{etyl|fro|en}} {{m|fro|absolution}}, from {{etyl|la|en}} {{m|la|absolūtiōnem}}, accusative singular of {{m|la|absolūtiō||acquittal}}, from {{m|la|absolvō||absolve}}. See also ''[[absolve]]''.

